<div><head>《詁幼》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.2">虴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.3">虴蜢也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.4">善跳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.5">蜢音猛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.6">陸德明《爾雅‧釋文》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.7">駽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.8">呼縣反。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-1a.9">《爾雅‧釋文》引呂忱、顏延之、荀楷。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.2">努，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.3">矢也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.4">《後漢書‧輿服志‧章懷太子》注引《幼誥》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.5">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.6">即《詁幼》也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.7">羅嗊歌曲。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.8">〈廣韻上聲一量嗊字〉注引《告幼童文》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.9">案：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1394_CHANT_001-2a.10">亦《詁幼》也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
